<br>
If someone would like to Roleplay a strong-armed melee cleric... all power to them.  They can just ignore all the advice.<br>
<br>
Good common-sense tactics on a blue server is also good common-sense tactics on FV.  'Roleplaying' server does not mean 'Free-for-all group tactics!  Everyone do whatever you feel like!  Cleric is tank!  Warrior is main healer!'  This would make the battles less than fun, as everyone would die all the time.<br>
<br>
I mean, if you want RP your warrior as an insane asylum escapee that thinks he is a healer... go ahead.  But you're not going to be very useful to anyone in an accual battle.  You're not going to go anywhere except back to bind point every five minutes.  And doing endless CRs is no fun... and it means less time to RP.<br>
